de/\"\n           rel=\"internal\">\n          Safety & Legal Guide (Canada)\n        </a>\n\n        <!-- Online Casinos -->\n        <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n           href=\"/canada-online-casinos/\"\n           rel=\"internal\">\n          Best Canadian Online Casinos\n        </a>\n\n        <!-- AI Bonus Finder -->\n        <a class=\"tcs-btn-secondary\"\n           href=\"/casino-bonus-finder/\"\n           rel=\"internal\">\n          AI Bonus Finder (Global Tool)\n        </a>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <p class=\"tcs-tagline\" style=\"margin-top:22px;\">\n        These resources help Canadian players compare bonuses, banking methods, payout reliability and \n        licensing standards across offshore and provincial online casinos with clarity and confidence.\n      </p>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>";
